These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, aconite, iris, orchid, dahlia, bellflower, rose
There are 7 different nationalities: australian, british, chinese, dutch, egyptian, french, german
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: june, august, january, september, november, october, february
House: ranch-style, cottage, wooden, colonial, victorian, palace, cape-cod
 1. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in november is the dutch##1
 3. the victorian house is the person who's birthday is in january##1
 4. the british is on the left of the palace house##1
 5. the australian is on the right of the german##1
 6. the person who growsaconite is the person who's birthday is in january##1
 7. the cape-cod house is on the right of the egyptian##1
 8. the colonial house is between the cape-cod house and the french##2
 9. the egyptian is on the right of the wooden house##1
10. the person who growsiris is in the middle##1
11. the person who's birthday is in june is the person who growsdahlia##1
12. the person who growsdahlia is the ranch-style house##1
13. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the chinese##1
14. the french is the wooden house##1
15. the palace house is on the left of the german##1
16. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
17. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the chinese##1
18. the person who growsrose is on the right of the egyptian##1
19. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the cottage house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Flower      | aconite  | bellflower        | dahlia | iris      | orchid     | amaryllis      | rose     |
| Nationality   | british | dutch         | german   | australian | french    | egyptian | chinese |
| Birthday         | january | november | june | august | february  | october  | september    |
| House     | victorian  | palace         | ranch-style     | cottage    | wooden | colonial     | cape-cod     |

