10. the fan of metal is between the fan of indie and the person traveling to paris##2
11. the fan of disco is the person traveling to rome##1
12. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
13. the fan of pop is between the person traveling to paris and the fan of reggae##2
